casebody.data:
Russell et al., Respondents, v. Allerton, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 14, 1890.)

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

No opinion. Beargument ordered on further briefs on points to be submitted in 10 days after notice of this decision. See 8 N. Y. Supp. 688.
